Preference.name: SubDeviceList
Preference.description: List of all possible sub devices, linked to one device

Preference.name: Type
Preference.description: Type of Subdevice. Could be : -actuator - Joint, JointHardness, Led, Power, Battery, UsSend, IrSend - Sensors - jointPosition, Current, FSR, ChestState, USReceived, Accelerometer, Gyrometer, Angle, Temperature, IrReceived, Switch, Battery

Preference.name: Device
Preference.description: Device Name where this subDevice is linked

Preference.name: SubDeviceNumber
Preference.description: Number of this subDevice in the Device (start from 1)

Preference.name: Ack
Preference.description: Number of answers from the device

Preference.name: Nack
Preference.description: Number of non-answers from the device

Preference.name: SensorType
Preference.description: The kind of sensor on the motor/joint. Strings values could be None, OneMRE, TwoMRE, Potar1, Potar2

Preference.name: positionChainMREJoint
Preference.description: Position if the MRE sensor if the joint in the MRE daisy chain (if there is one)

Preference.name: positionChainMREMotor
Preference.description: Position if the MRE sensor if the motor in the MRE daisy chain (if there is one)

Preference.name: GearRatio
Preference.description: The gear ratio of the joint

Preference.name: motorModel
Preference.description: The motor model of the joint

Preference.name: OtherMotorTransmission
Preference.description: percentage of second motor heat to take in consideration

Preference.name: XPosition
Preference.description: X position of the FSR in the ref of the foot

Preference.name: YPosition
Preference.description: Y position of the FSR in the ref of the foot

Preference.name: ncag
Preference.description: Delay before rising the variable gain

Preference.name: BatteryVoltageAfterLearning
Preference.description: Battery Voltage in V after last learning cycle

Preference.name: DelayForDischargeErrorReset
Preference.description: Delay in s for DischargeError Reset

Preference.name: CountOfCycleAfterLastLearning
Preference.description: Count of cycles after last learning cycle

Preference.name: DischargeOverCurrentAlarm14A
Preference.description: Discharge Over Current Alarm more than 14A

Preference.name: DischargeOverCurrentAlarm6A
Preference.description: Discharge Over Current Alarm more than 6A

Preference.name: CellValue
Preference.description: Cell Value of the subDevice (degre celcius)

Preference.name: Type
Preference.description: Type of device. Could be : MotherBoard, ChestBoard, MotorBoard, MotorBoardHand, MotorBoardFoot, TouchBoard, FaceBoard, USBoard, IntertialSensor, EarLeds

Preference.name: Bus
Preference.description: Bus where the device is. Could be : MotherBoard, MotherBoardI2C, Chest, ChestI2C, RS485Down, RS485Up, LeftHandI2C, RightHandI2C

Preference.name: Address
Preference.description: Slave number on the bus, from 0 to 127

Preference.name: ProgVersion
Preference.description: Version of the main program for the device

Preference.name: ChainResult
Preference.description: Version of the main program for the device

Preference.name: BodyNickName
Preference.description: Usual nick name of the robot

Preference.name: StructVersion
Preference.description: Version of the configuration struct for the device

Preference.name: BoardId
Preference.description: Version of the electronic board struct for the device

Preference.name: BoardId2
Preference.description: 2nd number version of the electronic board struct for the device

Preference.name: BootLoaderVersion
Preference.description: Version of the bootloader for the device

Preference.name: ProgVersion
Preference.description: Version of the main program for the device
